#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Mahāyaññavagga "
msgstr "5. A Great Sacrifice "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 48. Paṭhamasaññāsutta → saṅkhittasattasaññāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an7.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Paṭhamasaññāsutta "
msgstr "48. Perceptions in Brief "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.48:1.1"
msgid "“Sattimā, bhikkhave, saññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā honti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these seven perceptions, when developed and cultivated, are very fruitful and beneficial. They culminate in the deathless and end with the deathless. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.48:2.1"
msgid "Katamā satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.48:2.2"
msgid "Asubhasaññā, maraṇasaññā, āhāre paṭikūlasaññā, sabbaloke anabhiratasaññā, aniccasaññā, anicce dukkhasaññā, dukkhe anattasaññā. "
msgstr "The perceptions of ugliness, death, repulsiveness of food, dissatisfaction with the whole world, impermanence, suffering in impermanence, and not-self in suffering. "

msgctxt "an7.48:2.3"
msgid "Imā kho, bhikkhave, satta saññā bhāvitā bahulīkatā mahapphalā honti mahānisaṃsā amatogadhā amatapariyosānā”ti. "
msgstr "These seven perceptions, when developed and cultivated, are very fruitful and beneficial. They culminate in the deathless and end with the deathless.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.48:2.4"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

